{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2016-02-12-100sites-001-timer/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"43b4f4cf-5100-5d18-a714-f38fe76c3b0a","html":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Kamigami55/100sites/tree/master/001_Timer\" target=\"_blank\">Github</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://kamigami55.github.io/100sites/001_Timer/timer.html\" target=\"_blank\">Live Demo</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7fMXTrA.jpg\" alt=\"螢幕快照 2016-02-12 上午1.01.54.png\"></p>\n<p>一個很簡單的倒數計時器。</p>\n<p>使用了很基本的前端老三套：HTML、CSS、JavaScript，各一個檔案來完成這個計時器。</p>\n<p>關鍵的計時功能由window.setInterval(function, delay)來完成，正常使用沒問題。</p>\n<p>目前的問題是時間拉長以後就會產生時間誤差，並且當使用者切換到別的頁面後，此時Timer在背景執行，瀏覽器分配給setInterval的資源就會變少，倒數速度就會變非常慢，甚至完全停止，我目前還找不到解決方法。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2016-02-12-100sites-001-timer/","tagSlugs":["/tag/100-sites/","/tag/project/","/tag/web/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-02-12 15:56","description":"一個很簡單的倒數計時器。","tags":["100sites","Project","Web"],"title":"【100sites #001】Timer","socialImage":"https://i.imgur.com/7fMXTrA.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2016-02-12-100sites-001-timer/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2195764341","251939775","401334301"]}